## Status legend

- 🟢 stable: PRs that contradict this spec are rejected by default
- 🟡 evolving: under active iteration, review carefully
- 🔴 broken: known issue, fixes welcome

## Change protocol

- Trivial wording fix: edit in place, log "Last reviewed" update
- New edge case discovered: add row to §7, add test, no DECISIONS entry needed
- LLM role / model change: DECISIONS.md entry required + Linksee context note
- Response pattern change: DECISIONS.md entry required + Linksee caveat if it
  reverses a prior choice
- Status change 🟡 → 🟢: DECISIONS.md entry, reviewer approval
